    <li><strong>Communication sequences:</strong> Triggered emails and reminders throughout the customer journey</li>
    <li><strong>Document management:</strong> Customer portals with automated collection and validation</li>
    <li><strong>Proposal system:</strong> Template-based generation with dynamic pricing</li>
    <li><strong>Payment automation:</strong> Online collection with automatic reconciliation</li>
    <li><strong>Reporting:</strong> Scheduled reports and real-time dashboards</li>
